description: Deletes an endpoint for a model from Amazon Bedrock Marketplace.
requestSyntax: DELETE /marketplace-model/endpoints/endpointArn HTTP/1.1
requestParameters:

endpointArn

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the endpoint you want to delete.

Required: Yes
